<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6410719>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–16. Habitus of Copelatus in China. 13. C. nanlingensis sp. nov. (holotype ♂; Dadongshan, Guangdong); 14. C. oblitus (♂; Cotai Ecological Zone, Macao); 15. C. oblitus (♀; Lantau, Hongkong); 16. C. parallelus (♀; Shanghai). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6410719/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6410704>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5–8. Habitus of Copelatus in China. 5. C. diversistriatus sp. nov. (holotype ♂; Pu’er, Yunnan); 6. C. diversistriatus sp. nov. (♂; NE Mintaingbin Forest Camp, Myanmar); 7. C. felicis sp. nov. (holotype ♂; Baishui, Yunnan); 8. C. japonicus (♂; Shanghai). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6410704/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6412781>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39–50. Male genitalia of Copelatus. 39, 41, 43, 45, 47, 49. median lobe in lateral view; 40, 42, 44, 46, 48, 50. paramere. 39–40. C. japonicus (Shanghai); 41. C. malaisei (a. Gaoligongshan, Yunnan; b. Renjiafen, Yunnan); 42. C. malaisei (Renjiafen, Yunnan); 43–44. C. miaowangi sp. nov. (paratype, Liupanshui, Guizhou); 45–46. C. mopanshanensis sp. nov. (holotype, Mopanshan, Yunnan); 47–48. C. nanlingensis sp. nov. (holotype, Dadongshan, Guangdong); 49–50. C. oblitus (Macao). Scale bar 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6412781/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6412783>
    dc:description "FIGURES 51–62. Male genitalia of Copelatus. 51, 53, 55, 57, 59, 61. median lobe in lateral view; 52, 54, 56, 58, 60, 62. paramere. 51–52. C. parallelus (Yushuwan, Hunan); 53. C. puzhelongi sp. nov. (a. holotype, Pu’er, Yunnan; b. Huanglianshan, Yunnan; c. Houaphanh, Laos); 54. C. puzhelongi sp. nov. (holotype, Pu’er, Yunnan); 55–56. C. rimosus (Dali, Yunnan); 57. C. rosulae sp. nov. (a. holotype, Pianma, Yunnan; b. Kongshu, Yunnan); 58. C. rosulae sp. nov. (Kongshu, Yunnan); 59–60. C. sociennus (Hengqin Island, Guangdong); 61–62. C. tenebrosus (Hengqin Island, Guangdong). Scale bar 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6412783/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6411112>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21–24. Habitus of Copelatus in China. 21. C. sociennus (♂; Hengqin Island, Guangdong); 22. C. tenebrosus (♂; Hengqin Island, Guangdong); 23. C. tengchongensis sp. nov. (holotype ♂; Beihai, Yunnan); 24. C. tengchongensis sp. nov. (paratype ♀; Beihai, Yunnan). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6411112/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6411114>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25–28. Habitus of Copelatus in China. 25. C. weymarni (♂; Kaymanovka, Russia); 26. C. xiniudong sp. nov. (holotype ♂; Xiniudong, Guizhou); 27. C. zimmermanni (♀; Danxia Shan, Guangdong); 28. C. sp. (♀; Lantau, Hongkong). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6411114/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6410764>
    dc:description "FIGURES 63–70. Male genitalia of Copelatus. 63, 65, 67, 69. median lobe in lateral view; 64, 66, 68, 70. paramere. 63–64. C. tengchongensis sp. nov. (holotype, Beihai, Yunnan); 65–66. C. weymarni (Honshu, Japan); 67–68. C. xiniudong sp. nov. (holotype, Xiniudong, Guizhou); 69–70. C. zimmermanni (Danxiashan, Guangdong). Scale bar 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6410764/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6411116>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29–38. Male genitalia of Copelatus. 29, 31, 33, 35, 37. median lobe in lateral view; 30, 32, 34, 36, 38. paramere. 29–30. C. bacchusi (Hainan); 31. C. chinensis (a. Lakeshan, Zhejiang; b. Yanjiajie, Hunan; c. Tainmushan, Zhejiang); 32. C. chinensis (Tianmushan, Zhejiang); 33. C. dentatipenis sp. nov. (a. holotype, Jinggangshan, Jiangxi; b. Guadun, Fujian; c. Mangshan, Hunan); 34. C. dentatipenis sp. nov. (holotype, Jinggangshan, Jiangxi); 35–36. C. felicis sp. nov. (holotype, Baishui, Yunnan); 37. C. diversistriatus sp. nov. (a. holotype, Pu’er, Yunnan; aa. detail of lateral carina with spines; b. Attapeu, Laos; c. NE Mintaingbin Forest Camp, Myanmar); 38. C. diversistriatus sp. nov. (holotype, Pu’er, Yunnan). Scale bar 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6411116/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6410708>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–12. Habitus of Copelatus in China. 9. C. malaisei (♂; Tengchong, Yunnan); 10. C. malaisei (♀; Tengchong, Yunnan); 11. C. miaowangi sp. nov. (paratype ♂; Liupanshui, Guizhou); 12. C. mopanshanensis sp. nov. (paratype ♂; Mopan Shan, Yunnan). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6410708/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6410721>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–20. Habitus of Copelatus in China. 17. C. puzhelongi sp. nov. (holotype ♂; Pu’er, Yunnan); 18. C. puzhelongi sp. nov. (paratype ♀; Pu’er, Yunnan); 19. C. rimosus (♂; Dali, Yunnan); 20. C. rosulae (paratype ♂; Pianma, Yunnan). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6410721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6410698>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Habitus of Copelatus in China. 1. C. bacchusi (♂; Xishuangbanna, Yunnan); 2. C. chinensis (♂; Lankeshan, Zhejiang); 3. C. chinensis (holotype ♀ of C. collocallosus); 4. C. dentatipenis sp. nov. (holotype ♂; Jinggangshan, Jiangxi). Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6410698/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

